{"an3.122:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 3.122 ","an3.122:0.2":"12. Apayikavagga ","an3.122:0.3":"Moneyyasutta ","an3.122:1.1":"“Tinimani, bhikkhave, moneyyani. ","an3.122:1.2":"Katamani tini? ","an3.122:1.3":"Kayamoneyyam, vacimoneyyam, manomoneyyam. ","an3.122:1.4":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, kayamoneyyam? ","an3.122:1.5":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu panatipata pativirato hoti, adinnadana pativirato hoti, abrahmacariya pativirato hoti. ","an3.122:1.6":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, kayamoneyyam. ","an3.122:2.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, vacimoneyyam? ","an3.122:2.2":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu musavada pativirato hoti, pisunaya vacaya pativirato hoti, pharusaya vacaya pativirato hoti, samphappalapa pativirato hoti. ","an3.122:2.3":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, vacimoneyyam. ","an3.122:3.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, manomoneyyam? ","an3.122:3.2":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asavanam khaya anasavam cetovimuttim pannavimuttim dittheva dhamme sayam abhinna sacchikatva upasampajja viharati. ","an3.122:3.3":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, manomoneyyam. ","an3.122:3.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, tini moneyyaniti. ","an3.122:4.1":"Kayamunim vacimunim, ","an3.122:4.2":"cetomunim anasavam; ","an3.122:4.3":"Munim moneyyasampannam, ","an3.122:4.4":"ahu sabbappahayinan”ti. ","an3.122:4.5":"Dasamam. ","an3.122:4.6":"Apayikavaggo dutiyo. ","an3.122:5.0":"Tassuddanam ","an3.122:5.1":"Apayiko dullabho appameyyam, ","an3.122:5.2":"Anenjavipattisampada; ","an3.122:5.3":"Apannako ca kammanto, ","an3.122:5.4":"Dve soceyyani moneyyanti. "}